name: harvest your adoration two
description: pull on the skin tagged udders of pointless worship. until they excrete their sinewy threads into a slop bucket that you'll feast on for a week. pull until you can't pull anymore. milk them dry and kill their source before moving onto the next. let the rusted bucket be your burden. let the bucket be your prize. let the sour taste of empty adoration curdle in your stomach with last weeks failures.
